# Experimental!
IsDigit ← ⍣(1◌⋕|0)
Step ← |3.3 (
  ⊃(⊢°□⊢⊡|∘|⍜⊡⍚↻₁)                         # Take first of current row, rotate.
  ⨬(⊃(⋅∘|◌∪Step-@A)|⊃(⋅⊙∘|˜⊂⊙⋅⋅∘))⊸IsDigit # Stash if digit, else recurse.
)
PWheel₂₀ ← &p$"Seq: _ _"◌◌⍥Step20⊙⊙"" 0⟜∘
≡◇PWheel₂₀ {{"123"}{"1B2" "34"}{"1DD" "" "" "678"}{"1BC" "34" "5B"}}
